title: Ep 55: ANXIETY
description: CP gets deep on anxiety. Of all the emails that get submitted to TDB, the most common theme among them is depression and anxiety. Why do we have this and does it serve any sort of purpose in our lives? How the fuck do we just calm down?
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
